  "response": "Yes, there are a few Nintendo DS racing games that involve pit stops. One notable example is **\"Need for Speed: ProStreet\"**. In this game, pit stops are an integral part of the racing experience, where players must manage tire changes, repairs, and other adjustments during races.\n\nAnother game that might interest you is **\"F1 2009\"**. This Formula 1 racing game also includes pit stops, where players need to strategize their stops to maintain or improve their race position.\n\nBoth of these games provide a realistic racing experience with the strategic element of pit stops, making them suitable choices for your query on the Nintendo DS.",
